flavor_text_entries.leafgreen:
The dustlike scales covering its wings
are color-coded to indicate the kinds of
poison it has.
flavor_text_entries.red:
The dust-like
scales covering
its wings are color coded to
indicate the kinds
of poison it has.
flavor_text_entries.blue:

scales covering
its wings are color coded to
indicate the kinds
of poison it has.
flavor_text_entries.yellow:
The powdery scales
on its wings are
hard to remove. They also contain
poison that leaks
out on contact.
flavor_text_entries.gold:
When it attacks,
it flaps its large
wings violently to scatter its poi­
sonous powder all
around.
flavor_text_entries.silver:
The powder on its
wings is poisonous
if it is dark in color. If it is
light, it causes
paralysis.
flavor_text_entries.crystal:
The scales it
scatters will
paralyze anyone who touches them,
making that person
unable to stand.
flavor_text_entries.ruby:
VENOMOTH is nocturnal - it is a POKéMON
that only becomes active at night.
Its favorite prey are small insects that gather around streetlights,
attracted by the light in the darkness.
